### Reset Password
POST https://localhost:5001/auth/reset-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "your-reset-token-here",
  "newPassword": "NewPassword123"
}

### Validate Reset Token
GET https://localhost:5001/auth/validate-reset-token/your-reset-token-here